endpoints.description: Unstable Registers a prompt within Vellum and creates associated Vellum entities. Intended to be used by integration partners, not directly by Vellum users. Under the hood, this endpoint creates a new sandbox, a new model version, and a new deployment.
endpoints.name: Register Prompt

endpoints.description: Unstable Upserts a new scenario for a sandbox, keying off of the optionally provided scenario id. If an id is provided and has a match, the scenario will be updated. If no id is provided or no match is found, a new scenario will be appended to the end. Note that a full replacement of the scenario is performed, so any fields not provided will be removed or overwritten with default values.
endpoints.name: Upsert Sandbox Scenario

pathParameters.description: A UUID string identifying this sandbox.

endpoints.description: Unstable Upserts a new test case for a test suite, keying off of the optionally provided test case id. If an id is provided and has a match, the test case will be updated. If no id is provided or no match is found, a new test case will be appended to the end. Note that a full replacement of the test case is performed, so any fields not provided will be removed or overwritten with default values.
endpoints.name: Upsert Test Suite Test Case

pathParameters.description: A UUID string identifying this test suite.
